parameters.name: SCET_UTC
parameters.description: sample S/C event time UTC in YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sss format

parameters.name: AOBT
parameters.description:
APSS onboard time (AOBT) value of sample. This is the spacecraft
                        clock time useds by the APSS instruments.

parameters.description: IFG axis 3 data in nT with estimated offset of -139 nT subtracted

parameters.name: IFG_3
parameters.description: IFG axis 3 data in nT with estimated offset of -139 nT subtracted

parameters.name: Bx_SC
parameters.description: Spacecraft coordinate system Bx component in nT

parameters.name: By_SC
parameters.description: Spacecraft coordinate system By component in nT

parameters.name: Bz_SC
parameters.description: Spacecraft coordinate system Bz component in nT

parameters.name: |B|
parameters.description: Field magnitude equals sqrt(Bx^2 + By^2 + Bz^2)

parameters.name: SenTemp
parameters.description: Measured sensor temperature in deg C

parameters.name: estElcTmp
parameters.description: Estimated electronics temperature in deg C
